Features to impletion:
DNS problem diag, at least include these commands:
dns list		List our DNS, name and IP
  	list-views	List views on our DNS, and query-source used to test for each view
  	resolve		Resolve the gave name from our DNS
	public-resolve	Resolve the gave name from famous public DNS
	reverse-resolve	Resolve IP address to domain name, so called ARPA

